title: Big Fish Games-Fairy Island-Precracked - PsychoticOverlord
description:
The misfortune was connected on the island of fairies forgotten in the ocean.
Fairies were stolen by pirates and sharpened into magic diamond.
 For you one must pass the set of colorful levels in order to free fairies from the captivity and to ascend the throne on the island peace.
Special features of the game:

- the excellent drawing;
- the magic of fairies as;
- several regimes of game to the selection.

System requirements:

OS: Windows Of xP
CPU: 800 MHz
RAM: 256 MB
Video: 32 MB
DirectX: 9.0 or it is above

Language of the interface: English
